long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A powerful Chrome extension that utilizes a paraphrasing tool to enhance ChatGPT's answer, making them more natural and unique, with just single click.

With HumanFlow, you can generate high-quality content quickly and easily. Simply set your prompt, and the extension does the rest, without sacrificing quality.
